  <description>
    <p>Hand TeX uses machine learning to find the matching LaTeX symbol and also offers a searchable list of all symbols.</p>
    <p>It features over 3500 symbols and their variations, of which over 1700 are unique.</p>
    <p>It operates fully offline, no internet connection at all.</p>
  </description>
